br&gt;&lt;img src="https://people.com/thmb/7-LggJcl73od2Mzf4LdEQ8PNo6M=/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc():format(jpeg)/Gina-Carano-The-Mandalorian-041124-4a6216eea1cc41f3a6e7d68fa58e80c8.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 16 May 2026 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://people.com/gina-carano-controveries-fired-from-the-mandalorian-11976157</guid></item></channel></rss>